  "title": "Senior Marketing Executive #75374",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Financial Services</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Senior Marketing Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong East</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days, Mon - Fri (9.00am - 6.00pm) Sat (9.00am – 1.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and implement marketing strategies to boost sales in commercial vehicles, motor insurance, and loan brokerage.</li><li>Manage and coordinate marketing campaigns across digital, social, and traditional media.</li><li>Collaborate with the Sales & Marketing team to drive lead generation and achieve business targets.</li><li>Analyze market trends and consumer behavior to identify expansion opportunities.</li><li>Monitor and adjust marketing campaigns to optimize performance.</li><li>Foster and maintain relationships with key stakeholders such as clients, vendors, and partners.</li><li>Other duties assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Business, or related field.</li><li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Proven marketing experience, particularly in the automotive, insurance, or financial services industries.</li><li>Proficiency in digital marketing, including SEO, SEM, and social media.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75374 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
